    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Kamiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, F, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Upon completing this technique, the user sends a massive upheaval of paper and chakra towards his target. The paper projectiles pierce everything in the area of effect, dealing 7d6 point of piercing damage.<br><br>This technique cannot affect items bearing Chakra Symbols (such as an exploding tag or advanced seal)</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> 9 ranks Craft (Visual Arts)</p>\n<p><b>Empower:</b> The user may increase the damage dealt by this technique by 1 die of damage, up to a maximum of 1d6 per level at the cost of 2 points of chakra per die of damage.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> At the third step of mastery, this technique can affect items bearing Chakra Symbols (such as an exploding tag or advanced seal).</p>\n",
